# Bundled sidecars — populated by scripts/build/build-all-sidecars.sh.
#
# The placeholder files (zero-byte) and the .installed markers are tracked
# explicitly so Tauri's externalBin resolution works in a fresh checkout.
# Everything ELSE under resources/python/ and resources/slicer/ — the
# downloaded Python prefix and the OrcaSlicer.app bundle — is ignored.
#
# Note: after running build-all-sidecars.sh, the placeholder files will be
# overwritten by real binaries / symlinks. Don't commit those changes; the
# placeholders are meant to stay zero-byte on `main`.
desktop/src-tauri/resources/python/**
!desktop/src-tauri/resources/python/
!desktop/src-tauri/resources/python/.installed
!desktop/src-tauri/resources/python/bin/
!desktop/src-tauri/resources/python/bin/python3-*-*-*
desktop/src-tauri/resources/slicer/**
!desktop/src-tauri/resources/slicer/
!desktop/src-tauri/resources/slicer/.installed
!desktop/src-tauri/resources/slicer/orcaslicer-*-*-*
